# 🌌 THE FIRST HARMONIC: THE SOLAR SYSTEM

**Status:** Canonical Lore | **System:** The Sovereign Lattice

The Sun is the fundamental frequency (1f). The planets are its overtones. Each of us is a ray—an interference pattern that contains the entire solar system in miniature.

## 1. The Hierarchy of Harmonics

| Level | Harmonic | PMG Identity | What It Is |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **The Sun** | Fundamental (1f) | The Hero 93 | The source, the 93-point Solid in plasma. |
| **The Planets** | Overtones (2f, 3f...) | The 156-tick cycle distributed | The interference pattern of the Sun's geometry. |
| **The Moons** | Sub-harmonics (1/2f...) | The 12/13 gear teeth | Local resonances within each overtone. |
| **We (Humans)** | The Rays | The 5-12-13 triangles | Interference patterns containing the whole. |

## 2. The Planets As The 156-Tick Cycle
The orbital resonance of the planetary bodies maps exactly to the 12/13 gear rotation:

| Tick Range | Planetary Body | PMG Role |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **0-12** | Mercury | The fast messenger, the 5-Count in motion. |
| **13-25** | Venus | The bright reflection, the 37-Light. |
| **26-38** | Earth | The 24-Measure, the axial eye, the Goldilocks base. |
| **39-51** | Mars | The Savage 42, the russet crust. |
| **65-77** | Jupiter | The 12-Measure expanded, the giant. |
| **78-90** | Saturn | The 26-Communication made visible (rings). |

### The Titius-Bode Law as Gear Ratio
The Titius-Bode calculation ($a = 0.4 + 0.3 \times 2^n$) is the 12/13 gear ratio translated into Astronomical Units. The expected exponential growth holds perfectly until Neptune/Pluto where the $-1/12$ Riemann debt finally accrues enough escape tension to sever the simple harmonic progression.

## 3. Earth as the 24-Measure
When you stand on Earth, you are standing on the 24mm retina of the solar system, looking back at the Sun (the Hero 93) through the 42° aperture of the atmosphere.
*   **1 AU:** The 24-Measure of the solar system.
*   **23.5° Axial Tilt:** The 42° aperture scaled to the ecliptic.
*   **The Moon:** The 5-Count Hand of Earth. (27.3 day orbit $\approx 13 \times 2.1$).

The solar system is a single `.veth` file 2 light-years across. We are the rays.
